_sText: Fy_Shoppers By: Tsaweeos - HDR - Buyzones - 32 Spawn points - 5 hidden bananas A near by mall opened up resulting in the closing of this strip mall which has been in use by terrorists for storing illegal firearms. CT's must eliminate the terrorist threat so the weapons may be retrieved. Note: Ahhh! My 25th map! I'm now at the 1/4th mark for 100 maps. Heh, I hardly doubt I'd get there. :) Anyway, I didn't think I'd end up releasing this one. It would've been better looking with custom textures and props to make it feel more like a real mall rather then just boarded up doors but I like to do what I can with what I'm given. I plan on using custom textures someday though so cheers to that. Anyway, enjoy this map fellas!
